        <p class="section-sub">
          Every Rotacut cutter is built on six engineering principles that ensure maximum
          performance on every cut.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="usp-grid" style="max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;">
        <div class="usp-item">
          <div class="usp-number">01</div>
          <div class="usp-title">Sandvik Carbide Tips</div>
          <p class="usp-text">
            Extremely hard and durable tungsten carbide cutting teeth sourced from Sandvik — the
            world's leading carbide manufacturer — for the hardest drilling tasks.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="usp-item">
          <div class="usp-number">02</div>
          <div class="usp-title">Optimised Cutting Geometry</div>
          <p class="usp-text">
            Offset tooth positioning and continuous pre-cut design delivers the lowest heat
            development and burr-free finishes on every hole.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="usp-item">
          <div class="usp-number">03</div>
          <div class="usp-title">Precision Ground Shanks</div>
          <p class="usp-text">
            Weldon 19.05mm and Universal 31.75mm shank options with close-tolerance fitment for zero
            run-out and maximum concentricity.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="usp-item">
          <div class="usp-number">04</div>
          <div class="usp-title">Optimal Chip Removal</div>
          <p class="usp-text">
            Engineered spiral flute angles designed for maximum chip evacuation efficiency — keeping
            the cut clean, cool, and consistent.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="usp-item">
          <div class="usp-number">05</div>
          <div class="usp-title">Stability &amp; Durability</div>
          <p class="usp-text">
            Special alloy body with tapered inside fitment prevents the cutter from getting stuck —
            protecting both the cutter and your magnetic drill.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="usp-item">
          <div class="usp-number">06</div>
          <div class="usp-title">Complete Size Range</div>
          <p class="usp-text">
            Diameters from 11mm to 65mm, cutting depths from 25mm to 100mm. Custom sizes available
            on request for OEM and special applications.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

